// SD-024 Stage 2: the legacy RunOptions-typed dispatch entry points
// (RunViaService, RunViaServiceWith, runFixtureHarnessViaRunner,
// RunWithConfigViaService) live in service_run_legacy.go so this file
// can stay free of references to the legacy options struct.

